from fastbook import *
from fastai.vision.widgets import *

key = '1be3ada0f2a649d087e9fb39798485a0'
customConfigId = 'efb1b149-c219-4091-be6d-14a279c405c4'

def search_images_bing_new(key, term, customConfigId, min_sz=128):
	url = 'https://api.bing.microsoft.com/v7.0/custom/images/search?' + 'q=' + term + '&' + 'customconfig=' + customConfigId + '&' + 'count=150'
	r = requests.get(url, headers={'Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key': key})
	search_results = r.json()
	return L([img["thumbnailUrl"] for img in search_results["value"][:150]])

painters = 'C.G. Kratzenstein Stub', 'Nicolai Abildgaard', 'Otto Ludvig', 'Edvard Lehmann', 'Jens Juel'

path = Path('painters')

if not path.exists():
    path.mkdir()
    for o in painters:
        dest = (path/o)
        dest.mkdir(exist_ok=True)
        results = search_images_bing_new(key, f'{o}', customConfigId)
        download_images(dest, urls=results)

fns = get_image_files(path)

failed = verify_images(fns)

failed

failed.map(path.unlink)

painters = DataBlock(
    blocks=(ImageBlock, CategoryBlock), 
    get_items=get_image_files, 
    splitter=RandomSplitter(valid_pct=0.4, seed=42),
    get_y=parent_label,
    item_tfms=Resize(128))

dls = painters.dataloaders(path)

dls.valid.show_batch(max_n=10, nrows=1)

painters = painters.new(item_tfms=RandomResizedCrop(128, min_scale=0.3))
dls = painters.dataloaders(path)
dls.train.show_batch(max_n=4, nrows=1, unique=True)

painters = painters.new(item_tfms=Resize(128), batch_tfms=aug_transforms(mult=2))
dls = painters.dataloaders(path)
dls.train.show_batch(max_n=8, nrows=2, unique=True)

painters = painters.new(
    item_tfms=RandomResizedCrop(224, min_scale=0.5),
    batch_tfms=aug_transforms())
dls = painters.dataloaders(path)

learn = cnn_learner(dls, resnet50, metrics=error_rate)
learn.fine_tune(6)

from ipywidgets import *
from fastai.vision.all import *

path = Path()
path.ls(file_exts='.pkl')
learn_inf = load_learner(path/'export.pkl')

bt_upload = widgets.FileUpload()

bt_upload

bt_upload = SimpleNamespace(data = ['images/MystiskMaleri.PNG'])
img = PILImage.create(bt_upload.data[-1])

out_pl = widgets.Output()
out_pl.clear_output()
with out_pl: display(img.to_thumb(128,128))
out_pl

pred,pred_idx,probs = learn_inf.predict(img)

lbl_pred = widgets.Label()
lbl_pred.value = f'Prediction: {pred}; Probability: {probs[pred_idx]:.04f}'
lbl_pred
